4
00:00:13,640 --> 00:00:16,920
Grey hairs, wrinkles and poor eyesight,

5
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:20,719
are common signs that our body is growing old.

6
00:00:20,719 --> 00:00:23,960
Much as we'd like to, we can't avoid aging,

7
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:27,519
so it's important to stay healthy as we get older.

8
00:00:27,519 --> 00:00:30,879
In this programme, we'll be hearing about some new research,

9
00:00:30,879 --> 00:00:34,439
offering fresh advice on how to stay young at heart,

10
