BBCLearningEnglish.com.

81
00:04:59,559 --> 00:05:04,359
Okay, let's recap the new vocabulary we've learnt about staying young at heart,

82
00:05:04,359 --> 00:05:10,120
an idiom which means to think and behave in a youthful way, in spite of growing older.

83
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:17,160
People with a positive attitude feel hopeful, confident and focused on the good things in life.

84
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:22,840
Twin studies use twins to investigate the roles of genetics and environment in human development.

85
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:29,160
A Mediterranean diet describes the food typically eaten by people living in countries around

86
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:33,480
the Mediterranean Sea, including fresh vegetables, olive oil and fish.

87
